ch.nolix.core.container

Class List<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.core.container.List<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements of a List.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IContainer<E>, Clearable<List<E>>, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public final class List<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Clearable<List<E>>, IContainer<E>
    A List is a IContainer that can add elements at the begin or end. A List is clearable.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
